name: MOONAI
description: We’re a well known team in the crypto industry, our 3 previous projects have reach over 100x from presale within 3-4 weeks… MSI,MK,CroShow MK Moon AI is a blockchain-based AI project built on the BNB Chain (Binance Smart Chain). It positions itself as an "AI companion" that fuses advanced artificial intelligence with decentralized technology to pioneer "decentralized intelligence." At its core, it's a BNB Project centered around the MOONAI Token, which powers the ecosystem. The platform aims to leverage blockchain for secure, transparent AI interactions, though specific use cases like AI-driven trading, content generation, or DeFi integrations aren't deeply detailed on the site.The project emphasizes trust and security, boasting a "100% verified" ecosystem with audits and partnerships. It's currently in a promotional or early-stage phase, focusing on community building via social channels rather than full-fledged product demos.
